Hello and welcome to my channel! Thank you for dropping by! :)

I love DIY/crafting and doing some interesting stuffs. Crafting is not really my talent but it was my hobby. I just love creating things that makes me happy (hopefully you too!) 

DIY things makes me so inspired to be able to continue my hobby. And I really really love to share it with you guys. I can't say that I am an expert doing some DIY's, but all I can say is I love this things.

They say, in crafting there are no mistakes. Just make a unique creations and be happy with it.

I hope one day, I'll be able to make you inspired to do on what makes you really happy. Because I believe that "an expert in anything was once a beginner" and Do your best and let God do the rest

snippet.description:
Hello and welcome to my channel! Thank you for dropping by! :)

I love DIY/crafting and doing some interesting stuffs. Crafting is not really my talent but it was my hobby. I just love creating things that makes me happy (hopefully you too!) 

DIY things makes me so inspired to be able to continue my hobby. And I really really love to share it with you guys. I can't say that I am an expert doing some DIY's, but all I can say is I love this things.

They say, in crafting there are no mistakes. Just make a unique creations and be happy with it.

I hope one day, I'll be able to make you inspired to do on what makes you really happy. Because I believe that "an expert in anything was once a beginner" and Do your best and let God do the rest 


Favorite verse:
"Do your best and let God do the rest" - 
 "I can do all things through Christ who strengthens me" - Philippians 4:13
